# Canonical Policy Bridge

Use [AGENT.md](../../AGENT.md) as canonical policy.

1. Respect DDD and Hexagonal boundaries.
2. Use ACL gateways for cross-context operations.
3. Keep controllers thin and use-case driven.
4. Follow `Intake -> Plan -> Execute -> Verify -> Handoff` workflow.
5. Use skills from `.agents/skills` when applicable.
